msgid "Of course, you can pass `all` for the resource names, too. And if you feel lucky, brave, or both you can avoid the questions by using the `--force` flag like this:"
msgstr "Of course, you can pass `all` for the resource names, too. And if you feel lucky, brave, or both you can avoid the questions by using the `--force` flag like this:"

